PrecisAmendment to the AIRPORT TRAFFIC REGULATIONS adding Kuujjuaq to the list of airports for the Quebec Region at which the regulations apply setting out the requirements for the operation and control of motor vehicles, pedestrians, and domestic animals while on airport premises and deleting several airports from the list that have been transferred to the Government of the Northwest Territories.
RegistrationRegistration: SOR/ 1993-0027 Publication Date: 1993-02-10
Attachments
precis:
Amendment to the AIRPORT TRAFFIC REGULATIONS adding Kuujjuaq to the list
of airports for the Quebec Region at which the regulations apply setting
out the requirements for the operation and control of motor vehicles,
pedestrians, and domestic animals while on airport premises and deleting
several airports from the list that have been transferred to the
Government of the Northwest Territories.
